<a href="http://www.saleslogistix.com/company/contact.html">SalesLogistix</a> to
<a href="mailto:support@saleslogistix.com?subject=ChangeControl Product Inquiry">
acquire the product</a> under the terms that you need.</fieldset></p>
<p>Download the application as a package and install it.&nbsp; The package 
automatically creates a Custom App, Custom Tab, two Custom Objects, some reports, and a dashboard.&nbsp; There is no 
code involved here.</p>
<p>You'll need to create two Workflows for the initial and complete approval 
cycles, &nbsp; and you may want to modify the page 
layouts for searches.
</p>
