<p>Using the AppExchange, organizations can easily add new apps to their current salesforce.com deployments, run them alongside their existing on-demand applications, and easily customize them to meet their unique needs. The breadth of applications on the AppExchange including CRM and many other types of business apps is limited only by the imagination of its publishers and the on-demand community itself.</p>


